Usage: flipOrRotateObject [-help] [-group] [-keepRelative] {-flip <MX|MY> | -rotate <R90|R180|R270>} [-name <string> ]

-help                       # Prints out the command usage
-flip <MX|MY>               # flip axis (string, required)
-group                      # rotate all selected instance as a group
                            # (bool, optional)
-keepRelative               # call relative floorplan command (bool, optional)
-name <string>              # name of the Object you want to flip or rotate
                            # (string, required)
-rotate <R90|R180|R270>     # rotate angle (string, required)